Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.31,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.39,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,If we can't get the door open, then we're out of options!
